            <bug_when>2008-08-21 03:32:30 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>A table starts off with no row focus indicator.  As soon as the mouse moves over the table, the indicator appears.  There&#39;s then no way to remove it.  Ever.  Table needs a method to clear (remove) the focus indicator.

Additionaly, I&#39;d recommend that a property be added that causes the focus indicator to be automatically removed upon mouseout, the most common need for clearing the indicator.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
