            <thetext>- It is now possible to remove the row focus highlight programatically by
  calling table.clearFocusedRowHighlight();

- To cause the row focus highlight to clear automatically when the mouse
  leaves the table, use this:

    table.addListener(&quot;mouseout&quot;, table.clearFocusedRowHighlight);

Derrell</thetext>
